{"article_id":"EdY9WM1rF3ZDCa7j","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Al Qaeda in the Arabian Peninsula claimed responsibility Wednesday for last week 's rampage","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that killed 12 people at France 's Charlie Hebdo satirical magazine .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"The attack was years in the making ,","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"an AQAP leader said in a video ,","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"claiming","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"U.S.-born cleric Anwar al-Awlaki was the mastermind behind it .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"Al-Awlaki was the terror group 's spokesman","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"before a U.S. drone strike killed him in Yemen in 2011 .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"For days , intelligence analysts have been trying to piece together","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"whether the gunmen","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"who attacked the magazine","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"met him on trips to Yemen","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"-- a theory","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"that could be bolstered by the new video 's claim .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"AQAP did not claim responsibility for Friday 's deadly siege at a kosher grocery store in Paris ,","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"but praised it .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"French security services have identified a suspected accomplice in that attack ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"according to the French newspaper Le Parisien .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"Police sources","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"cited by the newspaper","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"said","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"one line of investigation is that the accomplice , a man from a Paris suburb , may have driven gunman Amedy Coulibaly to the kosher supermarket ,","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"where Coulibaly later shot dead four people .","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"Coulibaly was killed in a police raid","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"to end the siege .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"Said and Cherif Kouachi , the brothers","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"who","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"authorities say","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"were behind the Charlie Hebdo attack ,","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"also are dead .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"But investigators ' efforts","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"to track down possible suspects","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"tied to last week 's attacks","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"are continuing .","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"So is the magazine","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"that the terrorists targeted last week .","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"Charlie Hebdo 's new edition hit newsstands Wednesday","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"-- a week after authorities say","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"terrorists Said and Cherif Kouachi burst into its newsroom","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"and gunned down staffers .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"New Charlie Hebdo issue on sale","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"MUST WATCH New Charlie Hebdo issue on sale 01:50","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"The cover features a cartoon of the Prophet Mohammed","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"crying .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"All 3 million copies sold out quickly ,","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"but more copies are coming soon ,","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"the magazine said .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"The claim of responsibility for the deadly attack on the magazine came in a video","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"showing AQAP commander Nasr Ibn Ali al-Ansi , with pictures of the Kouachis in the background .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"`` When the heroes were assigned ,","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"they accepted .","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"They promised","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"and fulfilled , ''","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"al-Ansi said .","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"Who is AQAP terror group commander al-Ansi ?","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"Who is AQAP terror group commander al-Ansi ?","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"02:26","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"He praised the attack ,","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"it was revenge for Charlie Hebdo 's depictions of Mohammed .","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"Al-Ansi blamed not only Charlie Hebdo , but also France and the United States .","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"`` It is France","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"that has shared all of America 's crimes , ''","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"al-Ansi added .","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"`` It is France","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"that has committed crimes in Mali and the Islamic Maghreb .","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"It is France","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"that supports the annihilation of Muslims in Central Africa in the name of race cleansing . ''","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"( `` Islamic Maghreb '' refers to North Africa . )","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"`` It was a blessing from Allah '' that the kosher market siege ,","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"in which four hostages were killed ,","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"took place about the same time ,","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"al-Ansi said .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"U.S. authorities said","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"they think","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"the video is authentic .","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"But they were n't ready to say","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"that AQAP helped carry out the assault .","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"`` We 're not there yet .","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"There are good indicators ''","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"that the group was behind the attack ,","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"but the intelligence community is still assessing ,","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"a senior administration official told CNN .","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"Earlier in the day , U.S. National Security Council spokesman Alistair Baskey said","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"that , `` if genuine ,","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"this is only the latest example of the wanton brutality","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"that is al Qaeda 's calling card","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"and which it has visited upon innocents of all faiths . ''","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"Investigators believe","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"Cherif Kouachi left Yemen with as much as $ 20,000 from AQAP","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"to carry out attacks ,","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"a U.S. official said .","depth":6},{"id":98,"text":"Le Parisien 's report said","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"investigators identified Coulibaly 's suspected accomplice","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"using keys for a motorbike","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"discovered in an apartment","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"they raided over the weekend .","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"Terrorist 's hideout apartment raided","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"Terrorist 's hideout apartment raided","depth":14},{"id":108,"text":"01:41","depth":14},{"id":109,"text":"Also found inside the apartment ,","depth":13},{"id":110,"text":"according to Le Parisien :","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"a stash of weapons , explosives and two ISIS flags .","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"Coulibaly purportedly told authorities","depth":13},{"id":113,"text":"before he was killed","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"that he belonged to ISIS","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"Police also suspect","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"the man may have been responsible for shooting and wounding a jogger last week --","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"an attack","depth":14},{"id":118,"text":"that the Paris prosecutor has said","depth":15},{"id":119,"text":"could be tied to Coulibaly","depth":15},{"id":120,"text":"because the ammunition","depth":16},{"id":121,"text":"used","depth":16},{"id":122,"text":"was the same as ammunition","depth":16},{"id":123,"text":"found at the scene of the kosher market attack ,","depth":16},{"id":124,"text":"Le Parisien said .","depth":14},{"id":125,"text":"Paris police would not comment to CNN on the contents of the report .","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"Le Parisien says","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"Coulibaly 's accomplice ,","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"who the newspaper did not name ,","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"is suspected to have fled France , possibly for Syria .","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"Officials have also said","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"they believe","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"Hayat Boumeddiene , Coulibaly 's widow","depth":13},{"id":133,"text":"who may have played a role in the attacks ,","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"has fled to Syria .","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"With France on its highest level of alert , 10,000 troops have deployed across the country .","depth":8},{"id":136,"text":"Thousands of police officers are on patrol ,","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"including hundreds","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"assigned to protect Jewish schools .","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"Since the attacks , dozens of cases have been opened in France against people","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"accused of expressing support for terrorism since the attacks ,","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"the Justice Ministry said .","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"It 's unclear how many people are blamed for the 54 infractions .","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"The cases include investigations","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"involving phone threats , cyberattacks and Facebook posts ,","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"the ministry said .","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"Some are in prison","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"awaiting trial ,","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"some have already been convicted ,","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"and some have been released with a notice of a court date ,","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"ministry spokesman Pierre Rance said .","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"Justice Minister Christiane Taubira `` considers","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"that words or actions of a racist or anti-Semitic nature ,","depth":13},{"id":153,"text":"or that cause hateful , violent , or discriminatory behavior ,","depth":14},{"id":154,"text":"or advocate terrorism ,","depth":15},{"id":155,"text":"or target security forces","depth":15},{"id":156,"text":"must be fought and pursued with the utmost vigor , ''","depth":12},{"id":157,"text":"her office said in a statement .","depth":10},{"id":158,"text":"She `` asked prosecutors to exercise extreme reactivity in the conduct of public action against the perpetrators of such crimes , ''","depth":10},{"id":159,"text":"the statement said .","depth":10},{"id":160,"text":"With concerns on the rise ,","depth":9},{"id":161,"text":"a controversial French comedian was accused of publicly supporting terrorism ,","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"French media reported .","depth":10},{"id":163,"text":"Dieudonne M'bala M'bala ,","depth":11},{"id":164,"text":"known as Dieudonne ,","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"was arrested in Paris ,","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"according to media reports ,","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"which tied his arrest to a recent Facebook post from the comedian .","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"`` Je suis Charlie Coulibaly , ''","depth":12},{"id":169,"text":"the post said ,","depth":12},{"id":170,"text":"combined the last name of one of the terrorists","depth":13},{"id":171,"text":"involved in last week 's attacks","depth":13},{"id":172,"text":"with the widely used phrase","depth":13},{"id":173,"text":"expressing solidarity with victims","depth":13},{"id":174,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":10},{"id":175,"text":"French comic faces 7 years in prison for Facebook post","depth":10},{"id":176,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":9},{"id":177,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":10},{"id":178,"text":"French comic faces 7 years in prison for Facebook post","depth":10},{"id":179,"text":"02:26","depth":9},{"id":180,"text":"On Monday , Dieudonne issued a statement with his stance on the terror attacks .","depth":7},{"id":181,"text":"`` Since the beginning of last year , I have been treated as public enemy number one ,","depth":9},{"id":182,"text":"when all","depth":13},{"id":183,"text":"I try to do","depth":13},{"id":184,"text":"is make people laugh ,","depth":12},{"id":185,"text":"and laugh about death , ''","depth":11},{"id":186,"text":"he wrote in a letter to the French interior minister .","depth":10},{"id":187,"text":"`` Because death laughs at us all ,","depth":9},{"id":188,"text":"as Charlie knows now ,","depth":10},{"id":189,"text":"unfortunately . ''","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":379,"left":0,"right":378,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":378,"left":229,"right":377,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":229,"left":203,"right":228,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":197,"right":202,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":197,"left":191,"right":196,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":191,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":196,"left":194,"right":195,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":194,"left":192,"right":193,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":192,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":193,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":195,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":202,"left":200,"right":201,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":200,"left":9,"right":199,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":199,"left":198,"right":12,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":198,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":201,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":22